  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">3435c78a314f4d799a95cef</uuid>
  <does rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</does>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">We will not use cookies to collect personally identifiable information about visitors We will not share any information we collect with anyone outside of the National Archives The usage of cookies in this way is considered a Tier 2 under the Office of Management and Budget s Memorandum 10-22 Guidance for Online Use of Web Measurement and Customization Technologies If you wish to disable cookies and opt out of this process you can find opt-out instructions on usa gov Disabling cookies will not restrict your access to the core content of the website</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

